              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "62-SM-149",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.946
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Two circular 149Sm2O3 samples (The diameters of both",
                "  were 11.5 cm, the thicknesses of the forward and",
                "  backward were 0.739 and 1.236 mg/cm2) placed back-",
                "  to-back on the cathode of the ionization chamber.",
                " The aluminum backings foils were 0.10 mm in thickness."
              ]
